po" style="font-size: xx-small;">Available for sale   in the <a class="newsarchive" href="http://www.iccrom.org/eng/db_en/db_bookshop_detail.asp?txtID=142">bookshop</a>: € 20,00 Euro</span></td>               </tr><tr>                 <td colspan="2"><div class="linea"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><img alt="linea_news02" height="7" src="http://www.iccrom.org/images/design/linea02.gif" width="100%" /></span> </div></td>               </tr><tr>                 <td><div align="center" class="buttondb"><div class="new"><span style="font-size: xx-small;">NEW: ICS05 </span></div><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><a class="titnews" href="http://www.iccrom.org/pdf/ICCROM_ICS05_LegalFrameworkAfrica_en.pdf" target="_blank" title="pdf file">PDF</a></span><br /><span class="corpo" style="font-size: xx-small;">(1.1 Mb)</span></div></td>                 <td valign="top"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><a class="titnews" href="http://www.iccrom.org/pdf/ICCROM_ICS05_LegalFrameworkAfrica_en.pdf" target="_blank" title="Legal Frameworks for the Protection of Immovable Cultural Heritage in Africa">Legal Frameworks for the Protection of Immovable Cultural Heritage in Africa</a>  </span><span class="corpo" style="font-size: xx-small;">(pdf 1.1 Mb)<br />Ndoro, Webber;  Pwiti, Gilbert  (eds). ICCROM, 2005</span><span style="font-size: xx-small;">. </span><span class="corpo" style="font-size: xx-small;">(ICS05)</span><span style="font-size: xx-small;">                      </span><span class="corpo" style="font-size: xx-small;">Papers resulting from the AFRICA 2009 seminar on Legal Frameworks held in Zimbabwe in 2002. </span><br /><span class="corpo" style="font-size: xx-small;">Available for sale   in the <a class="newsarchive" href="http://www.iccrom.org/eng/db_en/db_bookshop_detail.asp?txtID=133">bookshop</a>: € 15,00 Euro</span></td>               </tr><tr>                 <td colspan="2"><div class="linea"><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><img alt="linea_news02" height="7" 